{"kind":"fwskill-signed","version":1,"author_pubkey":"0f5b2c14f816687780e10686e6834b5d6ccf90bdf18dca5a3dab358f86448b97","signed_at":"2026-06-16T20:16:29Z","source":"flowork","skills":[{"name":"circuit-breaker-agent","content":"---\nname: circuit-breaker-agent\ndescription: Mencegah retry loop berulang dengan tracking kegagalan consecutive tool/model dan auto-escalation saat threshold tercapai.\n---\n\n## Tujuan\nMelindungi agent dari stuck retry loops dengan circuit breaker yang trip ke escalation otomatis.\n\n## Konsep\n- **State tracking**: Simpan `failure_count` \u0026 `last_failure_time` per `(agent_id, tool_name, model_name)`.\n- **Trip condition**: Jika `failure_count \u003e= threshold` (default: 3), set `breaker_state = 'open'`.\n- **Escalation**: Saat open, route ke fallback handler atau human escalation.\n- **Recovery**: Auto-reset setelah `timeout_reset` atau manual intervention.\n\n## Tabel data helper (additive-only)\n```\ncircuit_breaker_state:\n  - id (INT pk)\n  - agent_id (TEXT)\n  - tool_name (TEXT)\n  - model_name (TEXT)\n  - failure_count (INT, default 0)\n  - last_failure_time (TIMESTAMP)\n  - breaker_state (TEXT: 'closed'|'open'|'half-open', default 'closed')\n  - created_at (TIMESTAMP)\n  - updated_at (TIMESTAMP)\n  \n  UNIQUE(agent_id, tool_name, model_name)\n```\n\n## Alur kerja\n\n### 1. Record failure\n```\n1. Hash key = (agent_id, tool_name, model_name)\n2. Query/upsert state row\n3. If exists: failure_count++, last_failure_time = now\n   Else: INSERT new row dengan failure_count=1\n4. Return breaker_state untuk decision logic agent\n```\n\n### 2. Check breaker status\n```\n1. Query state by hash key\n2. If breaker_state='open':\n   - Check elapsed time vs timeout_reset\n   - If elapsed \u003e timeout: set state='half-open', reset failure_count\n   - Else: REJECT request (escalate)\n3. Return {state, failure_count, can_retry}\n```\n\n### 3. Record success (reset)\n```\n1. Query state by hash key\n2. Set failure_count=0, breaker_state='closed'\n3. Update last_success_time\n```\n\n## Threshold \u0026 config (tunable)\n- `FAILURE_THRESHOLD`: 3 consecutive failures → trip\n- `TIMEOUT_RESET`: 60s before half-open retry\n- `HALF_OPEN_TIMEOUT`: 30s to validate recovery\n\n## Integration point\n- **Pre-tool call**: Check breaker → if open, escalate\n- **Post-tool call**: On failure, increment; on success, reset\n- **Agent loop**: Respect breaker state, don't retry open circuits\n","sig":"544fbdbf57a13baabacd68c30984075e0032c8139f17868229144961c04d4d35632fa0836be4ff52c50c19e8d46bacaaa1645caa18deecd2487014e7126c2d0c"}]}